pageTitle: High School Sports | Oct. 16 2013 football North Sevier-South Sevier | Deseret News
textBeforeTable: Rushing Individual stats South Sevier jumped out to an early 26-point lead and never looked back, cruising past North Sevier in region play. Devin Bishoff ran for two TDs, while Jaaron Nielsen caught two more touchdowns to lead the home team in the big win.
